706918f-b.title: Brooklyn: Strong Place - Degraw Street
706918f-b.text:
(1)
Streng Place, at the N.W. corner of Degraw Street, showing the Strong
Place Baptist Church.
February 21, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, showing also the S.W. corner. Ths church in this view was
completed in 1856.
October 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Cellection.
